{"tid":1779149,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來真係有套作品叫「圖書館戰爭」","createTime":"2019-12-11T13:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T13:34:48.000Z","uid":15224,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"729e388317814c898d6b36157aca9e17536e2b41","tid":1779149,"uid":15224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:10:36.000Z","msg":"《圖書館戰爭》（日語：図書館戦争），是日本作家有川浩所著的小說，以及根據小說改編而成的漫畫、電視動畫、劇場版動畫與真人版電影。小說插畫由徒花スクモ繪製。<br />\n<br />\n故事簡介<br />\n在架空世界的日本，為了公序良俗等理由，政府制定了侵犯人權的「媒體良化法」（媒體優質化法），並成立了「媒體良化委員會」（媒體優質化委員會）與「良化特務機關」（優質化特務機關）來進行媒體檢閱工作。與這個強權機關對抗的唯一組織，即為「圖書館」。一群熱愛圖書館自由的人們，武裝自己與良化機關進行戰爭，守護圖書館的自由。笠原郁在高中的某一天看到了想買的書，卻遇上了良化委員會的成員，這時卻出現了一名圖書隊員，使對方離開。西元2019年（正化31年），笠原郁加入了戰爭&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"ae0bbde89c1a5fd25441f6d087018b6c44121cb4","tid":1779149,"uid":134774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:11:35.000Z","msg":"西元2019年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1203f96ec41decccf9f75767afdb86d9695b31db","tid":1779149,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:11:52.000Z","msg":"抄狗狗錦滿的"},{"pid":"e7fc101fd50af23b78473c5fd0a1e26d58ed9bd0","tid":1779149,"uid":266176,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:13:29.000Z","msg":"其實好出名下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4937a3c7bd949c099d36f2bcb9238bb36afffc3","tid":1779149,"uid":176313,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:16:47.000Z","msg":"嗰陣睇覺得個設定好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef1f160e4f1b46b09e3d924ea078133263da27d","tid":1779149,"uid":21917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:18:32.000Z","msg":"好多年啦<img